<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7104] AddReplica Collection API call discards all the property prefix parameters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7104</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;CollectionsHandler.handleAddReplica&lt;/tt&gt; does not call &lt;tt&gt;copyPropertiesIfNotNull&lt;/tt&gt; . This means all the property prefix values are discarded. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s behaviour is documented in the ref guide &lt;a href=&quot;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/solr/Collections+API#CollectionsAPI-api_addreplica&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/solr/Collections+API#CollectionsAPI-api_addreplica&lt;/a&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;</description>
